    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdministratorView
    The AdministratorView class provides the user interface for the administrator of the hospital management system.
    AppointmentOutcomeRecord
    The AppointmentOutcomeRecord class manages the recording and retrieval of appointment outcomes within the hospital management system.
    AppointmentSlot
    The AppointmentSlot class manages appointment scheduling within the hospital management system.
    AppointmentSlotController
    The AppointmentSlotController class manages appointment scheduling, rescheduling, cancellation, and status updates for appointments in the hospital management system.
    DataInitializer
    The DataInitializer class is responsible for loading patient and staff details, as well as medical records from CSV files into their respective data structures.
    Doctor
    The Doctor class represents a doctor in the hospital management system.
    DoctorView
    The DoctorView class provides the user interface for the doctor in the hospital management system.
    Main
    The Main class serves as the entry point for the Hospital Management System application.
    MedicalRecord
    The MedicalRecord class represents a patient's medical record in the hospital management system.
    MedicalRecordController
    The MedicalRecordController class manages the medical records and user information for patients in the hospital management system.
    Medicine
    The Medicine class represents a medicine in the hospital management system.
    MedicineController
    The MedicineController class manages the inventory of medicines in the hospital management system.
    Patient
    The Patient class represents a patient in the hospital management system.
    PatientView
    The PatientView class is responsible for handling the patient's view of the Hospital Management System.
    PharmacistView
    The PharmacistView class provides the user interface for the pharmacist in the hospital management system.
    Staff
    The Staff class represents a staff member in the hospital management system.
    StaffController
    The StaffController class manages the staff records in the hospital management system.
    User
    The User class represents a user in the hospital management system.
    UserController
    The UserController class provides functionalities for managing user accounts, including prompting for password changes and updating user information in CSV files.
